<h1 id="chapter2-虚幻引擎入门">Chapter2. 虚幻引擎入门</h1>
<h2 id="21-向当前项目添加资产">2.1 向当前项目添加资产</h2>
<ol>
<li><code>内容浏览器</code>-<code>添加/导入</code>：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023164753.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>从其他项目中迁移<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023173545.png" alt="" loading="lazy">选择要迁移的对象，在<code>细节</code>面板中，点击<code>在内容浏览器中查看</code>，<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023173726.png" alt="" loading="lazy">右键-资产操作-迁移(拷贝)<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023173817.png" alt="" loading="lazy">系统显示该资产所包含的子对象，点击确定，然后在弹出的资源管理器中中选择目标工程的Content文件夹。</li>
<li>导入选项：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023174534.png" alt="" loading="lazy">在当前工程内容浏览器中，进入目标路径，右键，选择导入...</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="22-设置玩家出生点">2.2 设置玩家出生点</h2>
<p>Press <kbd>End</kbd> ，<mark>使出生点碰撞体与地平面对齐</mark>.</p>
<h2 id="23-在场景中模拟真实天空效果">2.3 在场景中模拟真实天空效果</h2>
<ol>
<li>将视觉效果中的天空大气拖入到场景中<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023181257.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>将光源中的定向光源拖入到场景中<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023181324.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
打开定向光源的细节面板，找到<code>大气与云</code>菜单，勾选<code>大气太阳光</code>选项：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023181510.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li><strong>此时定向光源的方向即为太阳光照射方向</strong>，使用旋转手柄转动定向光源的投射方向即可模拟一天不同时刻的太阳光照变化。<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023181732.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="24-视觉效果">2.4 视觉效果</h2>
<h3 id="场景中的光照强度">场景中的光照强度：</h3>
<ol>
<li>定向光源强度（默认10）</li>
<li>天光强度（默认1）</li>
</ol>
<h3 id="天光光源颜色影响场景色偏">天光光源颜色影响场景色偏：</h3>
<ol>
<li>当定向光源强度0，天光强度1，天光光源颜色为白色时：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023231657.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>当定向光源强度0，天光强度1，天光光源颜色为红色时：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023231721.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>当定向光源强度4，天光强度1，天光光源颜色为白色时：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023232038.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>当定向光源强度4，天光强度1，天光光源颜色为红色时：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023232112.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<p>所以，天光更像是环境光或反射光</p>
<h3 id="后期处理体积简要介绍postprocessvolume">后期处理体积简要介绍（PostProcessVolume）</h3>
<p>关于镜头曝光的选项：<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233407.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<ol>
<li>最低亮度0.25+最高亮度0.8的效果：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023232918.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>取消最高、最低亮度限制的效果：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233041.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>最低亮度1.0+最高亮度1.0的效果：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233144.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<h3 id="光束遮挡与泛光">光束遮挡与泛光</h3>
<p>定向光源细节面板中的光束菜单：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233725.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<ol>
<li>光束遮挡×，光束泛光×：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233846.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>光束遮挡√，光束泛光×：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233859.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>光束遮挡×，光束泛光√：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233913.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
<li>光束遮挡√，光束泛光√：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023233947.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<p>最后根据想要的效果调节泛光范围、颜色和最高亮度。</p>
<h3 id="光源的移动性">光源的移动性</h3>
<ol>
<li><strong>静态</strong>（完全烘焙，渲染速度最快）</li>
<li><strong>固定</strong>（部分烘焙，动态阴影来自可移动对象）</li>
<li><strong>可移动</strong>（完全动态，全场景动态阴影，渲染速度最慢）</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="25-编辑蓝图">2.5 编辑蓝图</h2>
<p>对场景中蓝图实例的蓝图类进行编辑：</p>
<ol>
<li>在场景中选中目标对象</li>
<li>在<code>大纲</code>或<code>细节面板</code>中找到<code>编辑蓝图</code>：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211023235028.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></li>
</ol>
<h2 id="26-初次debug">2.6 初次Debug</h2>
<blockquote>
<p>在导入UELearningKit的场景到第三人称模板空项目后，运行该场景，<strong>发现鼠标无法控制主角的左右转向</strong>，上下转向是OK的。如何解决？</p>
</blockquote>
<p>打开该场景的角色的蓝图类，进入<code>事件图表</code>，找到报错（WARNING!）:<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211024000236.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<pre><code>报错：引用了未知的轴TurnRight
</code></pre>
<h3 id="解决方法">解决方法：</h3>
<p>打开项目<code>设置</code> - <code>输入</code> - <code>绑定</code> - <code>轴映射</code>，<strong>新建一个新的轴映射：TurnRight</strong>，键值为<strong>鼠标X</strong>：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211024000915.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
回到蓝图类的事件图表，点击编译：<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211024001047.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211024001106.png" alt="" loading="lazy"><br>
输入轴的WARNING消失，问题得到解决。</p>
