        <title type="html"><![CDATA[GitPage + Gridea 搭建个人博客记录]]></title>
        <id>https://autolins.github.io/post/git-page-gridea-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke-ji-lu/</id>
        <link href="https://autolins.github.io/post/git-page-gridea-da-jian-ge-ren-bo-ke-ji-lu/">
        </link>
        <updated>2021-10-18T09:41:08.000Z</updated>
        <summary type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文记录了如何使用GitPage和开源博客框架Gridea来搭建简易个人博客的方法，实验参考Gridea官方文档，实验过程供新手朋友参考。</p>
]]></summary>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>本文记录了如何使用GitPage和开源博客框架Gridea来搭建简易个人博客的方法，实验参考Gridea官方文档，实验过程供新手朋友参考。</p>
<!-- more -->
<h2 id="0-环境准备">0. 环境准备</h2>
<ol>
<li>Git安装</li>
<li>Gridea安装</li>
</ol>
<h2 id="1-官方文档">１. 官方文档</h2>
<p><a href="https://gridea.dev/gridea-start/">🤗 快速上手 | Gridea</a></p>
<h2 id="2实验记录">2.实验记录</h2>
<h3 id="2-1-创建一个仓库token">2-1. 创建一个仓库Token</h3>
<p>进入Github，进入<strong>Settings/ Developer settings/Personal access tokens</strong> ，点击<strong>Generate new token</strong>。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="1"><img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211018183030.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>在<strong>New personal access token</strong>中，<strong>勾选repo的所有权限</strong>，最好给这个Token批注用途信息，生成后务必记录下来，<span style="border-bottom:2px solid red; font-weight: bold;">一旦网页关闭将无法再次查看此Token</span>。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="2"><img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018163705.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="3"><img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018163950.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<h3 id="2-2-创建一个仓库存放网站文件">2-2. 创建一个仓库，存放网站文件</h3>
<p>创建一个<strong>公开</strong>仓库，名为<code>GitHub用户名.github.io</code>。</p>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="4"><img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018164910.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<blockquote>
<p><strong>如何查看GitHub用户名？</strong><br>
登录GitHub，Settings/Account/Change username。</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="2-3-gridea远程设置">2-3. Gridea远程设置</h3>
<p>进入Gridea，点击<strong>远程设置</strong>，根据步骤2-2的仓库名称和GitHub用户名称和步骤2-1的Token完成配置即可</p>
<blockquote>
<p>分支：默认填写master<br>
域名：如果没有购买域名的话，填写步骤2-2的仓库名称即可</p>
</blockquote>
<figure data-type="image" tabindex="5"><img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018165251.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></figure>
<p>点击<strong>检测远程链接</strong>，出现如下Toast即为成功。<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018165512.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<h3 id="2-4-gridea同步">2-4. Gridea同步</h3>
<p>点击Gridea中的<strong>同步</strong>按钮即可。初次部署等待几分钟之后就可以去浏览器访问了，默认地址为你在第 3 步所填写的域名。<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018165847.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>出现如下Toast即为成功。<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018165904.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>同步成功后，在浏览器输入域名，即可看到初步搭建的博客效果，<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/Pasted%20image%2020211018170045.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p>对应的，回到步骤2-2在GitHub创建的仓库，也可以发现该仓库也多了许多网站的文件。<br>
<img src="https://pico-blogimage1-1303850390.cos.ap-guangzhou.myqcloud.com/pico-blogimage/20211018182802.png" alt="" loading="lazy"></p>
<p><strong>至此，使用Gridea搭建博客的实验圆满成功~</strong></p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
